{
  "text": "Results of power calculations indicated that a sample size of 35 in each group was required to achieve a power of more than 0.81, based on previous publications studying the effects of sildenafil vs placebo and using the IIEF index. [CITATION_1] The data are expressed as mean±SEM and analyzed with repeated-measures analysis of variance, with a post hoc analysis using a Fisher probable least-significant differences test (StatView; SAS Institute, Cary, NC). PϽ.05 was considered statistically significant.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "68111482"
